83def49311af165ff2d98fe4b8d6691","tid":983164,"uid":139064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T17:26:17.000Z","msg":"阿爸拎緊綜援，阿媽有案底，罰一千，冇坐監，案底已喪失時效，我自己就冇馬會户口，冇借過財仔，冇翻過工，冇信用卡，冇犯過罪。<br />\n咁既情況，過唔過到PI既vetting？<br />\n<br />\n{如案底已喪失時效，該罪犯等同沒有被定罪一樣，因此，如他在求職時被僱主或其他人詢問有無犯過刑事罪，他可立即回答：「無」。該人不得因為沒有披露其案底而被解僱。}<br />\n<br />\n我係咪可以填表時寫阿媽冇犯過刑事罪？<br />\n<br />\n真係好唔開心，我真係好想做PI，如果真係有人答到我，我真係會好感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T03:08:20.000Z","msg":"VETTING關綜援咩事，如果你窮佢唔請你，簽名果個都比人告歧視啦<br />\n<br />\n有案底無關係，唔係黑社會相關罪行就得<br />\n<br />\n佢vet你係睇你有無人派黑社會入去做卧底，唔係犯黑社會相關罪行無影響<br />\n<br />\n我勸你咪搏，佢門面果套好講誠信，你比人周到一次佢有record你呢世都唔洗再黎"},{"pid":"c3c67888c87941d65cf3f7b03e1387c26635f74e","tid":983164,"uid":200052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T03:09:05.000Z","msg":"登報斷絕關係就可以"},{"pid":"9fec8314b6c977d389585409a5b164f0ffc5b75a","tid":983164,"uid":167428,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T03:17:46.000Z","msg":"希望你肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdfd4e6ac6821e0720c9d5f0d91d2231a1959463","tid":983164,"uid":139064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fec8314b6c977d389585409a5b164f0ffc5b75a","tid":983164,"uid":167428,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T03:17:46.000Z","msg":"希望你肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T03:21:13.000Z","msg":"頂你啦 touchwood <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">不過我都預左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"4c721eb7c3c3e27947d7df8191e5be01b6c53428","tid":983164,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3